Definition: denying or questioning the tenets of especially a religion
Example: a skeptical approach to the nature of miracles
Synonyms: skeptical, noun, person, skeptic, cognition, skepticism, sceptical, scepticism, sceptic, unbelieving, denying, or, questioning, the, tenets, of, especially, a, religion, approach, to, nature, miracles
Category: adj.all
